17. Flexible Box Layout(布局)

    justify-content(左右) — controls alignment of all items on the main axis.
    align-items(上下) — controls alignment of all items on the cross axis.
    align-self(上下) — controls alignment of an individual flex item on the cross axis.
    align-content(上下) — described in the spec as for “packing flex lines”; controls space between flex lines on the cross axis.
 
    flex: flex-grow || flex-shrink || flex-basis
    flex-flow: flex-direction || flex-wrap
    order: 
    visibility: 

